verbose_text: GRHL2 expression was detected in cultured human corneal epithelial cells derived from limbal epithelial stem cells and in a spontaneously immortalized human corneal epithelial cell line with progenitor like characteristics, but was absent in corneal endothelial tissue, an immortalized cell line of human corneal endothelial origin, and stromal fibroblasts by RT-PCR (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY B).
